員可以不停針對案中主要證人"},{"pid":"3d3ea7b6599f0bc0955bcba53f6409ea6a059558","tid":885164,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"明知身有屎<br />\n<br />\n真相(石)屎中尋"},{"pid":"b7ae75e1b7e487981cb6da7d3037633d55ea2e64","tid":885164,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"鑿開佢嚟睇咪得，點解要浪費時間？"},{"pid":"28ce5fe22bc26d495c3b2186c3891ea1d22a7695","tid":885164,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"講錯區域就推翻哂話所有野都係幻想出黎<br />\n法律面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684a0c00013febd2facad5d003021d45b8da5895","tid":885164,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"律師就係門口狗,收狗糧幫主人咬對家證人好正常<br />\n<br />\n但委員會班帝制派平時食公帑,關鍵時間針對潘先生做咩"}]}